Just want to give yall a heads up. I've got a shitload of content created and scheduled out on instagram to funnel creators into booking 1:1 shortform coaching with me. Thats why I've been so quiet. Just want you all to be aware that after this week, priority discounted 1 on 1s with me and creator breakdowns wont be available. I'll still be in here like normal though.

Before I do that, I want to give you guys the opportunity. If you want a private channel breakdown or 1:1 time with me before things get crazy, DM me. If you're worried about budget, just say so and we'll work something out. Not saying any of you need it at all. I just want to make sure you guys are taken care of before a crap load of people start funneling in. That said, keep up the watermarks lol

@VIP

@Levi (Pixel Beef/Hidden Signal) @AndreS The 'FAKE' comments absolutely come with storytelling. Somewhere in the course I talk about it. I always look at it like "Do you yell 'fake' at the screen when you saw Toy Story? Because that's what you're doing right now."

This is something that catches you off guard at first but then when you don't see it in the comments, it's kinda upsetting. lol Because it didn't create enough of a reaction from them to say fake in the first place.

Hate is nothing but good news.
